    "This effect is intensified as the feeding rate increases, leading to larger stresses in the extruded filament.",
    "This exhibits the fact that stress formation, initiated after melting at the hotend, continues during extrusion, and its understanding is crucial for predicting the shape-morphing mechanism of the final part.",
